name: Giran
Lore: 'Kajain''sa''Nikto. Loyal to Jabba. Helps tend the rancor with Malakili. Hopes to snare a krayt dragon someday and pit it against the rancor.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +3 when defending a battle at a Jabba''s Palace site. May forfeit in place of one of your alien leaders present who was ''hit'' by a weapon, restoring that leader to normal.',
